# ASAccessoryEventType.accessoryChanged

**Case**

The properties of an accessory changed.

## Declaration

```swift
case accessoryChanged
```

## Accessory events

- **ASAccessoryEventType.accessoryAdded**: The session added an accessory.
- **ASAccessoryEventType.accessoryRemoved**: The session removed an accessory.
